<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Code envoyé</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            width: 400px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #0d6efd;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .timer {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc3545;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #0d6efd;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #0b5ed7;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Code d’accès généré</h1>
        <p>Un code temporaire a été envoyé.</p>
        <p>Il est valide pour <span class="timer">15 minutes</span>.</p>
        <a href="/admin">Entrer le code</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
